  CMake modules.

  19 Dec 2013; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> llvm-9999.ebuild:
  Symlink the LLVM gold plugin to bfd-plugins directory to enable LLVM object
  support in various binutils tools, bug #462554.

